# RL Connect-4

Train a self-play Connect-4 agent with:
- PettingZoo (`connect_four_v3`)
- Stable-Baselines3 + sb3-contrib `MaskablePPO`
- Sparse rewards (`-1/0/+1`)
- Legal-action masking
- TensorBoard metrics for reward and win-rate baselines

## Quickstart

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -e ".[dev]"
python scripts/train_self_play.py --config configs/train_self_play.yaml
```

## TensorBoard

```bash
tensorboard --logdir runs
```
